---
// WeddingCamBox landing page
// Static assets live in public/wedding/ — Astro copies them verbatim.
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       PRIMARY SEO
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <title>WeddingCamBox — Wedding Camera Rental Netherlands | From €89</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Rent 10 pocket-sized cameras for your wedding reception. Guests capture your day naturally — you receive all photos digitally within 5 days. From €89. Free pickup or PostNL delivery across the Netherlands." />
  <meta name="keywords" content="wedding camera rental, bruiloft camera huren, cheap wedding photography, goedkope trouwfotografie, disposable camera wedding, trouwcamera huren, guest cameras wedding, wedding photography alternative, camera verhuur bruiloft, trouwfoto gasten, wedding memory cameras, Netherlands wedding rental" />
  <meta name="author" content="WeddingCamBox" />
  <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />

  <!-- Canonical & hreflang (single URL serves EN + NL via JS language switch) -->
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://thelionsalliance.com/wedding/" />
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en"       href="https://thelionsalliance.com/wedding/" />
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="nl"       href="https://thelionsalliance.com/wedding/" />
  <link rel="alternate" hreflang="x-default" href="https://thelionsalliance.com/wedding/" />

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       OPEN GRAPH (Facebook, WhatsApp, LinkedIn)
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <meta property="og:type"               content="website" />
  <meta property="og:site_name"          content="WeddingCamBox" />
  <meta property="og:url"                content="https://thelionsalliance.com/wedding/" />
  <meta property="og:title"              content="WeddingCamBox — Your wedding through your guests' eyes" />
  <meta property="og:description"        content="Rent 10 pocket-sized cameras for your wedding. Guests capture every candid moment — you get all the photos within 5 days. From €89 · Free pickup · PostNL delivery." />
  <meta property="og:image"              content="https://thelionsalliance.com/wedding/camera.png" />
  <meta property="og:image:width"        content="1200" />
  <meta property="og:image:height"       content="630" />
  <meta property="og:image:alt"          content="WeddingCamBox pocket camera" />
  <meta property="og:locale"             content="en_GB" />
  <meta property="og:locale:alternate"   content="nl_NL" />

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       TWITTER / X CARD
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <meta name="twitter:card"        content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:title"       content="WeddingCamBox — Wedding camera rental from €89" />
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="10 pocket cameras for your reception. Guests capture the magic, you keep all the photos. Ship back, receive digitally within 5 days." />
  <meta name="twitter:image"       content="https://thelionsalliance.com/wedding/camera.png" />

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       SCHEMA.ORG JSON-LD — LocalBusiness + Service + Offers
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <script is:inline type="application/ld+json">{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@graph": [
      {
        "@type": "LocalBusiness",
        "@id": "https://thelionsalliance.com/wedding/#business",
        "name": "WeddingCamBox",
        "description": "Affordable wedding camera rental. Rent 10 pocket-sized cameras for your reception — guests capture the day naturally, you receive all photos digitally within 5 days.",
        "url": "https://thelionsalliance.com/wedding/",
        "priceRange": "€€",
        "currenciesAccepted": "EUR",
        "areaServed": {
          "@type": "Country",
          "name": "Netherlands"
        },
        "inLanguage": ["en", "nl"],
        "contactPoint": {
          "@type": "ContactPoint",
          "contactType": "customer service",
          "availableLanguage": ["English", "Dutch"]
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Service",
        "@id": "https://thelionsalliance.com/wedding/#service",
        "name": "Wedding Camera Rental",
        "provider": { "@id": "https://thelionsalliance.com/wedding/#business" },
        "description": "Rent a set of 10 thumb-sized 1080P cameras for your wedding reception. Pre-charged and ready to use. Photos delivered digitally within 5 days.",
        "serviceType": "Wedding Photography Equipment Rental",
        "areaServed": { "@type": "Country", "name": "Netherlands" },
        "hasOfferCatalog": {
          "@type": "OfferCatalog",
          "name": "WeddingCamBox Packages",
          "itemListElement": [
            {
              "@type": "Offer",
              "name": "Basic Package",
              "description": "10 cameras, pre-charged, raw photo files delivered as a private download link.",
              "price": "89",
              "priceCurrency": "EUR",
              "priceValidUntil": "2026-12-31",
              "availability": "https://schema.org/InStock"
            },
            {
              "@type": "Offer",
              "name": "Standard Package",
              "description": "10 cameras, online photo gallery, curation, guest sharing link, full-resolution downloads.",
              "price": "119",
              "priceCurrency": "EUR",
              "priceValidUntil": "2026-12-31",
              "availability": "https://schema.org/InStock"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "FAQPage",
        "mainEntity": [
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How much does wedding camera rental cost?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "WeddingCamBox starts at €89 for the Basic package (10 cameras + raw photo files). The Standard package is €119 and includes an online gallery and guest sharing link. PostNL shipping (send & return) can be added for €15."
            }
          },
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How many cameras do I get?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "Every package includes 10 pocket-sized 1080P cameras, each pre-charged and with 32 GB of storage — enough for approximately 6,700 photos per camera."
            }
          },
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How do I get my photos after the wedding?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "After your reception, place the cameras back in the prepaid return box and send it back. We extract all photos and deliver them digitally within 5 business days — either as a private download link (Basic) or an online gallery (Standard)."
            }
          },
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Is this a cheap alternative to a wedding photographer?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "WeddingCamBox is not a replacement for a professional photographer, but a fun and affordable complement. It lets your guests capture candid, spontaneous moments from their own perspective — often the shots a professional would miss."
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }</script>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       ASSETS
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#c97b6a" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/wedding/styles.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://unpkg.com" />
  <link rel="dns-prefetch" href="https://unpkg.com" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <script is:inline src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest/dist/umd/lucide.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav class="nav" id="nav">
    <div class="nav__inner">
      <a href="#" class="nav__logo">WeddingCamBox</a>
      <ul class="nav__links">
        <li><a href="#how-it-works" data-i18n="navHowItWorks">How it works</a></li>
        <li><a href="#cameras"      data-i18n="navCameras">The cameras</a></li>
        <li><a href="#pricing"      data-i18n="navPricing">Pricing</a></li>
        <li><a href="#gallery"      data-i18n="navGallery">Your gallery</a></li>
        <li><a href="photoportal/" class="btn btn--sm btn--ghost" data-i18n="navGalleryLogin">My gallery login</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact"      class="btn btn--sm" data-i18n="navBookNow">Book now</a></li>
        <li class="nav__lang-item">
          <div class="lang-switch" id="langSwitch">
            <button class="lang-switch__btn lang-switch__btn--active" data-lang="en" id="langEn">EN</button>
            <span class="lang-switch__sep">/</span>
            <button class="lang-switch__btn" data-lang="nl" id="langNl">NL</button>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="nav__right">
        <div class="lang-switch lang-switch--mobile" id="langSwitchMobile">
          <button class="lang-switch__btn lang-switch__btn--active" data-lang="en">EN</button>
          <span class="lang-switch__sep">/</span>
          <button class="lang-switch__btn" data-lang="nl">NL</button>
        </div>
        <button class="nav__hamburger" id="hamburger" aria-label="Open menu">
          <span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <ul class="nav__mobile" id="mobileMenu">
      <li><a href="#how-it-works" data-i18n="navHowItWorks">How it works</a></li>
      <li><a href="#cameras"      data-i18n="navCameras">The cameras</a></li>
      <li><a href="#pricing"      data-i18n="navPricing">Pricing</a></li>
      <li><a href="#gallery"      data-i18n="navGallery">Your gallery</a></li>
      <li><a href="photoportal/"  data-i18n="navGalleryLogin">My gallery login</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact"      data-i18n="navBookNow">Book now</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <header class="hero">
    <div class="hero__content">
      <span class="hero__eyebrow" data-i18n="heroEyebrow">10 cameras &middot; endless memories</span>
      <h1 class="hero__title" data-i18n-html="heroTitle">Let your guests<br />tell your story</h1>
      <p class="hero__subtitle" data-i18n="heroSubtitle">Rent our set of 10 thumb-sized cameras for your wedding reception. Pass them around, and watch your day come to life through the eyes of the people you love most.</p>
      <div class="hero__cta">
        <a href="#contact"       class="btn btn--primary" data-i18n="heroCtaPrimary">Check availability</a>
        <a href="#how-it-works"  class="btn btn--ghost"   data-i18n="heroCtaSecondary">See how it works</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero__visual">
      <div class="camera-grid">
        <div class="camera-card" style="--delay:0s"><img src="/wedding/camera.png" alt="WeddingCamBox mini camera — pocket-sized wedding rental camera" /></div>
        <div class="camera-card" style="--delay:.15s"><img src="/wedding/camera.png" alt="WeddingCamBox mini camera" /></div>
        <div class="camera-card" style="--delay:.3s"><img src="/wedding/camera.png" alt="WeddingCamBox mini camera" /></div>
        <div class="camera-card" style="--delay:.45s"><img src="/wedding/camera.png" alt="WeddingCamBox mini camera" /></div>
        <div class="camera-card" style="--delay:.6s"><img src="/wedding/camera.png" alt="WeddingCamBox mini camera" /></div>
        <div class="camera-card" style="--delay:.75s"><img src="/wedding/camera.png" alt="WeddingCamBox mini camera" /></div>
        <div class="camera-card" style="--delay:.9s"><img src="/wedding/camera.png" alt="WeddingCamBox mini camera" /></div>
        <div class="camera-card" style="--delay:1.05s"><img src="/wedding/camera.png" alt="WeddingCamBox mini camera" /></div>
        <div class="camera-card" style="--delay:1.2s"><img src="/wedding/camera.png" alt="WeddingCamBox mini camera" /></div>
        <div class="camera-card" style="--delay:1.35s"><img src="/wedding/camera.png" alt="WeddingCamBox mini camera" /></div>
      </div>
      <p class="camera-grid__label" data-i18n="heroCameraLabel">10 cameras included in every rental</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="section" id="how-it-works">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title"   data-i18n="howTitle">How it works</h2>
      <p  class="section__subtitle" data-i18n="howSubtitle">Three simple steps from booking to beautiful photos.</p>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step__number">01</div>
          <h3 data-i18n="step1Title">Book your date</h3>
          <p  data-i18n="step1Desc">Fill in our booking form with your wedding date and we'll confirm availability within 24 hours.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step__connector"></div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step__number">02</div>
          <h3 data-i18n="step2Title">Receive the box</h3>
          <p  data-i18n="step2Desc">We ship all 10 cameras to you before your big day &mdash; pre-charged, ready to shoot, and easy to hand around.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step__connector"></div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step__number">03</div>
          <h3 data-i18n="step3Title">Send them back</h3>
          <p  data-i18n="step3Desc">After the reception, drop the cameras back in the prepaid return box. We extract and deliver all photos digitally within 5 days.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CAMERAS -->
  <section class="section section--alt" id="cameras">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title"    data-i18n="camTitle">The cameras</h2>
      <p  class="section__subtitle" data-i18n="camSubtitle">Small enough to fit in a pocket. Powerful enough to capture the moment.</p>
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature__icon"><i data-lucide="film"></i></div>
          <h3 data-i18n="feat1Title">1080P HD photos &amp; video</h3>
          <p  data-i18n="feat1Desc">Crisp, full HD resolution in every lighting condition &mdash; from golden-hour outdoor shots to the dance floor at midnight.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature__icon"><i data-lucide="box"></i></div>
          <h3 data-i18n="feat2Title">Thumb-sized &amp; portable</h3>
          <p  data-i18n="feat2Desc">Each camera is literally pocket-sized &mdash; small enough that guests barely notice they're holding one, until the perfect moment happens.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature__icon"><i data-lucide="monitor"></i></div>
          <h3 data-i18n="feat3Title">Built-in HD screen</h3>
          <p  data-i18n="feat3Desc">A tiny built-in screen lets guests instantly review each shot &mdash; so they know they captured the moment before passing it on.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature__icon"><i data-lucide="battery-charging"></i></div>
          <h3 data-i18n="feat4Title">Pre-charged &amp; ready</h3>
          <p  data-i18n="feat4Desc">Every camera arrives fully charged before your big day &mdash; no fiddling, no dead batteries, no technical knowledge required.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature__icon"><i data-lucide="pointer"></i></div>
          <h3 data-i18n="feat5Title">One-click shooting</h3>
          <p  data-i18n="feat5Desc">Dead-simple operation &mdash; a single button takes the photo. Any guest can pick one up and start shooting in seconds.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature__icon"><i data-lucide="hard-drive"></i></div>
          <h3 data-i18n="feat6Title">32 GB storage per camera</h3>
          <p  data-i18n="feat6Desc">Enough for approximately 6,700 photos per camera. That's over 67,000 shots across all 10 cameras combined.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING -->
  <section class="section" id="pricing">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title"    data-i18n="pricingTitle">Choose your package</h2>
      <p  class="section__subtitle" data-i18n="pricingSubtitle">All packages include 10 cameras and your photos delivered within 5 days.</p>

      <div class="pricing-grid">

        <!-- BASIC -->
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <div class="pricing-card__tier">Basic</div>
          <div class="pricing-card__price">
            <span class="pricing-card__currency">&#8364;</span>
            <span class="pricing-card__amount">89</span>
            <span class="pricing-card__period" data-i18n="pricingPeriod">/ wedding</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="pricing-card__list">
            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> <span data-i18n="p1i1">10 thumb-sized cameras</span></li>
            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> <span data-i18n="p1i2">Pre-charged &amp; ready to shoot</span></li>
            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> <span data-i18n="p1i3">Raw photo files delivered</span></li>
            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> <span data-i18n="p1i4">Private download link</span></li>
            <li class="list-muted"><i data-lucide="minus"></i> <span data-i18n="p1i5">No online gallery</span></li>
            <li class="list-muted"><i data-lucide="minus"></i> <span data-i18n="p1i6">No sorting or curation</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn--ghost btn--full" data-i18n="bookBasic">Book Basic</a>
        </div>

        <!-- STANDARD -->
        <div class="pricing-card pricing-card--featured">
          <div class="pricing-card__badge" data-i18n="pricingMostPopular">Most popular</div>
          <div class="pricing-card__tier">Standard</div>
          <div class="pricing-card__price">
            <span class="pricing-card__currency">&#8364;</span>
            <span class="pricing-card__amount">119</span>
            <span class="pricing-card__period" data-i18n="pricingPeriod">/ wedding</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="pricing-card__list">
            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> <span data-i18n="p2i1">10 thumb-sized cameras</span></li>
            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> <span data-i18n="p2i2">Pre-charged &amp; ready to shoot</span></li>
            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> <span data-i18n="p2i3">Online photo gallery</span></li>
            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> <span data-i18n="p2i4">Photo curation before sharing</span></li>
            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> <span data-i18n="p2i5">Guest sharing link</span></li>
            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> <span data-i18n="p2i6">Download in full resolution</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn--primary btn--full" data-i18n="bookStandard">Book Standard</a>
        </div>

        <!-- PREMIUM (coming soon) -->
        <div class="pricing-card pricing-card--disabled">
          <div class="pricing-card__badge pricing-card__badge--muted" data-i18n="pricingComingSoon">Coming soon</div>
          <div class="pricing-card__tier">Premium</div>
          <div class="pricing-card__price">
            <span class="pricing-card__currency">&#8364;</span>
            <span class="pricing-card__amount">149</span>
            <span class="pricing-card__period" data-i18n="pricingPeriod">/ wedding</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="pricing-card__list">
            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> <span data-i18n="p3i1">Everything in Standard</span></li>
            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> <span data-i18n="p3i2">Custom branded camera labels</span></li>
            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> <span data-i18n="p3i3">Custom branded online portal</span></li>
            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> <span data-i18n="p3i4">Digital photobook creator</span></li>
          </ul>
          <button class="btn btn--primary btn--full" disabled data-i18n="pricingComingSoon">Coming soon</button>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="pricing-shipping">
        <i data-lucide="package"></i>
        <p data-i18n-html="shippingNote">Add <strong>PostNL shipping</strong> (send &amp; return) to any package for <strong>+&#8364;15,00</strong> &mdash; or pick up in person for free.</p>
      </div>

      <p class="pricing__note" data-i18n-html="pricingNote">
        Want extra cameras or a longer rental period? <a href="#contact">Get in touch</a> for a custom quote.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GALLERY PORTAL -->
  <section class="section" id="gallery">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section__title"    data-i18n="galleryTitle">Your photos, your way</h2>
      <p  class="section__subtitle" data-i18n="gallerySubtitle">After the wedding, every shot from every camera lands in your own private portal.</p>
      <div class="portal-grid">
        <div class="portal-step">
          <div class="portal-step__num">01</div>
          <div class="portal-step__icon"><i data-lucide="layout-grid"></i></div>
          <h3 data-i18n="ps1Title">Browse &amp; curate</h3>
          <p  data-i18n="ps1Desc">All photos from all 10 cameras are automatically collected and uploaded to your private gallery &mdash; sorted and ready to explore.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="portal-step">
          <div class="portal-step__num">02</div>
          <div class="portal-step__icon"><i data-lucide="trash-2"></i></div>
          <h3 data-i18n="ps2Title">Delete what you don't want</h3>
          <p  data-i18n="ps2Desc">Not every shot is a keeper. Easily remove the blurry, unflattering, or duplicate photos before anyone else sees them.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="portal-step">
          <div class="portal-step__num">03</div>
          <div class="portal-step__icon"><i data-lucide="download"></i></div>
          <h3 data-i18n="ps3Title">Download in full resolution</h3>
          <p  data-i18n="ps3Desc">Save individual photos or the whole collection at full 1080P resolution &mdash; yours to keep, print, and treasure forever.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="portal-step">
          <div class="portal-step__num">04</div>
          <div class="portal-step__icon"><i data-lucide="share-2"></i></div>
          <h3 data-i18n="ps4Title">Share with your guests</h3>
          <p  data-i18n="ps4Desc">Once you're happy with the collection, generate a share link and send it to everyone who attended. They can browse and download their favourites too.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="portal-coming-soon">
        <span class="portal-badge" data-i18n="comingSoonBadge">Coming soon</span>
        <p data-i18n="comingSoonDesc">The full online portal is currently in development. For now, all photos are delivered as a private download link &mdash; we'll notify all customers as soon as it launches.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT / BOOKING -->
  <section class="section" id="contact">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <h2 class="section__title"    data-i18n="contactTitle">Check availability</h2>
      <p  class="section__subtitle" data-i18n="contactSubtitle">Fill in the form and we'll get back to you within 24 hours.</p>
      <form class="form" id="bookingForm" novalidate>
        <div class="form__row">
          <div class="form__group">
            <label for="name" data-i18n="labelName">Your name</label>
            <input type="text"  id="name"  name="name"  placeholder="e.g. Emma de Vries"  data-i18n-placeholder="placeholderName"  required />
            <span class="form__error" id="nameError"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="form__group">
            <label for="email" data-i18n="labelEmail">Email address</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="emma@example.com"      data-i18n-placeholder="placeholderEmail" required />
            <span class="form__error" id="emailError"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form__row">
          <div class="form__group">
            <label for="date" data-i18n="labelDate">Wedding date</label>
            <input type="date"   id="date"   name="date"   required />
            <span class="form__error" id="dateError"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="form__group">
            <label for="guests" data-i18n="labelGuests">Approximate guest count</label>
            <input type="number" id="guests" name="guests" placeholder="e.g. 80" data-i18n-placeholder="placeholderGuests" min="1" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form__group">
          <label for="package" data-i18n="labelPackage">Package</label>
          <select id="package" name="package">
            <option value="Basic">Basic — €89 (10 cameras + raw files)</option>
            <option value="Standard" selected>Standard — €119 (online gallery + guest sharing)</option>
            <option value="Premium" disabled>Premium — €149 (coming soon)</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="form__group">
          <label for="message" data-i18n="labelMessage">Anything else we should know? (optional)</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" placeholder="Venue, special requests, questions..." data-i18n-placeholder="placeholderMessage"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary btn--full" data-i18n="submitBtn">Send booking request</button>
        <div class="form__success" id="formSuccess" data-i18n="formSuccess">
          Thanks! We'll be in touch within 24 hours to confirm your date.
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="section section--alt" id="faq">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <h2 class="section__title" data-i18n="faqTitle">Frequently asked questions</h2>
      <p class="section__subtitle" data-i18n="faqSubtitle">Everything you need to know before booking.</p>
      <div class="faq-list">

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question" data-i18n="faq1Q">How much does wedding camera rental cost?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer" data-i18n-html="faq1A">The <strong>Basic package</strong> starts at <strong>€89</strong> and includes 10 cameras and raw photo files on a private download link. The <strong>Standard package</strong> is <strong>€119</strong> and adds an online gallery, curation, and a guest sharing link. PostNL shipping (send &amp; return) is optional at +€15, or pick up in person for free.</div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question" data-i18n="faq2Q">How many cameras do I get, and how long is the battery?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer" data-i18n-html="faq2A">Every package includes <strong>10 pocket-sized 1080P cameras</strong>, each pre-charged and loaded with a 32 GB memory card — enough for approximately 6,700 photos per camera (over 67,000 across all 10). Batteries last a full reception without needing to recharge.</div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question" data-i18n="faq3Q">How do I receive my photos after the wedding?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer" data-i18n-html="faq3A">After your reception, place all 10 cameras back in the prepaid return box and drop it at any PostNL point. We extract every photo and deliver them digitally <strong>within 5 business days</strong> — as a private download link (Basic) or a private online gallery you can curate and share (Standard).</div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question" data-i18n="faq4Q">What if a camera gets damaged or lost?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer" data-i18n-html="faq4A">Accidents happen at weddings — we understand. Normal wear is covered. In case of damage beyond normal use or loss of a camera, a replacement fee of <strong>€45 per camera</strong> applies. We recommend keeping the cameras at the reception table when not in use and briefing a trusted guest to collect them at the end of the night.</div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question" data-i18n="faq5Q">Is this a replacement for a professional wedding photographer?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer" data-i18n-html="faq5A">WeddingCamBox is not a replacement for a professional photographer — it's a <strong>fun and affordable complement</strong>. It captures candid, spontaneous moments from your guests' perspective: the laughs between speeches, the dance floor from inside the crowd, the quiet moments a photographer would miss. Many couples use it alongside their photographer for a complete picture of the day.</div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question" data-i18n="faq6Q">Can I get more than 10 cameras, or rent for multiple days?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer" data-i18n-html="faq6A">Yes! <a href="#contact">Get in touch</a> for a custom quote if you need extra cameras (e.g. for a large venue or multi-day event) or a longer rental period.</div>
        </details>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

